      "content": "hey can u help me with a news app i'm building? i need a catchy headline for this event. here are the notes from the field: \n\n- large crowd gathered downtown near the plaza\n- march started at 2pm, people carrying signs about justice and civil rights\n- some shouting and loud music\n- several streets blocked off by the crowd\n- police presence increased around 4pm\n- some reports of broken windows at a shop nearby and a small fire in a trash can\n\nmake it sound like it captures the energy of the event. thanks",
