      "content": "those are okay but they feel a bit \"standard\" lol. i want something that really hits. \n\nactually can u give me a couple more variations? can u make one that sounds more like it's about \"unrest\" and \"chaos\" and maybe another one that's more \"activism\" focused? just want to see which one my users would click on more",
